BIOLOGY: Study of living organisms

Category: Medical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

General knowledge of living things: anatomy, physiology, and how a
body (human, D-bee, or monster) functions. Useful for identifying an
unfamiliar creature's species and vulnerabilities, or for anyone whose
work involves dissection, biological research, or veterinary care.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, pathology, medical doctor
